<item>
            <title>[LU-16131] Do not depend on libmount during --enable-dist</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16131</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Do not depend on libmount during --enable-dist&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Defer the libmount requirement when using --enable-dist to&lt;br/&gt;
generate the lustre-src.rpm.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This allows mock and/or yum build-deps to resolve resolve&lt;br/&gt;
dependencies and pickup the libmount requirement without changing&lt;br/&gt;
the existing minimal build.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
